# nonebot-plugin-tts-gal

_✨ [Nonebot2](https://github.com/nonebot/nonebot2) 基于nonebot2和vits的本地化角色语音合成插件 ✨_

<p align="center">
  <a href="https://github.com/dpm12345/nonebot_plugin_tts_gal/blob/master/LICENSE">
